import React, { useContext } from 'react';

import {
    Container,
    ButtonAlertMessage,
    ContainerHeader,
    TextMessage,
    ContainerListCards,
    ContainerBody,
    ContainerListCalls,
    Title,
} from './styles'

import { AntDesign } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { Button } from 'react-native';

import { Profile } from '../../components/Profile'
import { ListCardsCategory } from '../../components/CategoryLists/ListCardsCategory'
import { ListCallsCategory } from '../../components/CategoryLists/ListCallsCategory'
import {firebase} from '../../service/FirebaseDB'

import { useNavigation, ParamListBase } from "@react-navigation/native"
import { DrawerNavigationProp } from "@react-navigation/drawer";

import { AuthContext } from '../../context/AuthContext';

export function Home() {

    const { signOut,} = useContext(AuthContext)

    const navigation = useNavigation<DrawerNavigationProp<ParamListBase>>()

    async function relogar() {
        await signOut()
    }

    return (
        <Container>

            <ContainerHeader>
                <Profile
                    onPress={() => navigation.openDrawer()}
                    date='Terça, 11 de maio'
                    hellow='Olá,'
                    strong='Nome do médico' />
                <ButtonAlertMessage>
                    <TextMessage>Aproveite seu 1 mês grátis!</TextMessage>
                    <AntDesign name="close" size={24} color="#7C7B7B" />
                </ButtonAlertMessage>
            </ContainerHeader>

            <ContainerBody>

                <ContainerListCards showsHorizontalScrollIndicator={false} horizontal>
                    <ListCardsCategory type="chamadas" title="Pedir mentoria" />
                    <ListCardsCategory type="chamadas" title="Meus chamados" />
                    <ListCardsCategory
                        onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Profile')}
                        type="dados"
                        title="Meus dados" />
                </ContainerListCards>

                <ContainerListCalls>
                    <Title>Histórico de chamadas</Title>
                    <ListCallsCategory
                        name="Naiara, 18"
                        message="Aguardando atendimento..."
                        date="Hoje"
                        onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Chat')} />
                </ContainerListCalls>

                <Button
                    title='Sair'
                    onPress={() => relogar()}
                />

            </ContainerBody>

        </Container>
    )
}
